# CryptoBuddy - Rule-based Cryptocurrency Advisor Chatbot

**Theme:** "Your First AI-Powered Financial Sidekick!" ðŸŒŸ

## What it is
A beginner-friendly rule-based chatbot (Python) that analyzes a small, predefined cryptocurrency dataset and gives simple advice based on profitability (price trends, market cap) and sustainability (energy use, sustainability score).

## Files
- `cryptobuddy.py` â€” main chatbot script and demo run
